      "retweeted_tweet_id": null,
      "text": "As @Sec_Noem and I continue our border sector visits, we met with Tucson Sector agents to personally thank them for their service and commitment to our nation. The visit concluded with a press conference at the border, joined by @CBPCommissioner Rodney Scott, highlighting the U.S. Border Patrol’s accomplishments over the past year. Following the press conference, three Tucson Sector agents were honored with the Newton-Azrak Award, the U.S. Border Patrol’s highest accommodation, for their bravery and heroism.",
      "text_resolved": "As @Sec_Noem and I continue our border sector visits, we met with Tucson Sector agents to personally thank them for their service and commitment to our nation. The visit concluded with a press conference at the border, joined by @CBPCommissioner Rodney Scott, highlighting the U.S. Border Patrol’s accomplishments over the past year. Following the press conference, three Tucson Sector agents were honored with the Newton-Azrak Award, the U.S. Border Patrol’s highest accommodation, for their bravery and heroism.",
